<StoryStep title={'"Peachtree"'} mediaFirst>
	<Canvas slot="media" fill fitScale class="cluster">
		{/* drop <Item><Image …/></Item> cut-outs here, position with ?edit */}
	</Canvas>

	<p>Atlanta's future site sat right between these two tribes.</p>
	<p>
		On the Muscogee side stood a village called Standing Peachtree—and that's
		where every Peachtree street in the city gets its name.
	</p>
	<p>The most-repeated word in Atlanta belongs to a place the city erased.</p>
</StoryStep>
